eeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Payload Valid?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"a64a6f14-630f-2383-304b-495b90cce1d5","name":"Note: Stamp & Shape Lead"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Payload Valid?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.leadId }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Route by Work Type · ②→ Record Rejected Input","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"3f040f49-878a-52b4-23fd-86ccad2a33e8","name":"Note: Payload Valid?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Rejected Input\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,1030],"id":"18f6c985-9e87-fd9f-6267-0ea6334df68e","name":"Note: Record Rejected Input"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Route by Work Type\n\nRoutes each item to one of 3 lanes: mql, sql + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Process 'mql' → HubSpot · ②→ Fast-Track 'sql' + Alert · ③→ Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"e076daea-ea70-c051-7698-3cd015966e4a","name":"Note: Route by Work Type"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Process 'mql' → HubSpot\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Routed Work · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,250],"id":"c5135816-b289-aa93-e7e1-d36ace65110b","name":"Note: Process 'mql' → HubSpot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fast-Track 'sql' + Alert\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Routed Work · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,760],"id":"4d9e2287-6a01-29ef-a80f-beeff4d68f18","name":"Note: Fast-Track 'sql' + Alert"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Routed Work · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,1270],"id":"360e1a9b-dd90-2bae-5cd3-400f3c615f99","name":"Note: Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Merge Routed Work\n\nRejoins 3 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Align Field Names","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,520],"id":"9ba036a8-6f7e-da6f-004a-b7115377e05d","name":"Note: Merge Routed Work"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Align Field Names\n\nNormalizes field names so every source feeds the same downstream schema.\n\nNext: Stamp Processing Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"1d491c2b-9a4d-eb46-a4d4-4f18bed61248","name":"Note: Align Field Names"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Processing Time\n\nStamps `processedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Tag Pipeline Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"49878f73-a53d-c366-78a8-1cc8e2a4a888","name":"Note: Stamp Processing Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\nShapes the item: writes `pipeline`, `version`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"da12ffd8-b5c1-c772-9f6e-6f9a758af606","name":"Note: Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (HubSpot)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"5eaef850-dc7c-508f-93ea-cc84e76f4dcc","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (HubSpot)\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Outlook · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"898338ed-ff7e-b902-9b14-5038ba4edbe1","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (HubSpot)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Outlook\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"78ebe28d-66c3-1b93-d209-7db6835094c2","name":"Note: Send Summary to Outlook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,1540],"id":"d114b92a-a677-259e-04a6-f8520b5fb08e","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,1540],"id":"c1d625bf-8d0c-a926-2198-42968b1a97c1","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Qualify inbound leads with HubSpot and Outlook end to end\n\n**Pattern:** Lead Capture & Routing · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Form\n\n## What it does\nQualify inbound leads with HubSpot and Outlook end to end. It starts from a hosted form submission.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual capture forms is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nNew Lead Form Submission → Stamp & Shape Lead → Payload Valid? → Route by Work Type → Process 'mql' → HubSpot → Merge Routed Work → Align Field Names → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to lead capture & routing without manual effort\n- Anyone automating capture forms in sales\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n- Improves response time\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: HubSpot private-app token; Microsoft OAuth2; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"b20f34d6-26dd-9a83-4cd8-817a1e3ef8d4","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-290],"id":"dce023b2-03dd-1e40-784b-e77d93c43e55","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your capture forms process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-290],"id":"75242ff2-b46b-4178-5fc3-aee449fc1277","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"New Lead Form Submission":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp & Shape Lead","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp & Shape Lead":{"main":[[{"node":"Payload Valid?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Payload Valid?":{"main":[[{"node":"Route by Work Type","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Record Rejected Input","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Route by Work Type":{"main":[[{"node":"Process 'mql' → HubSpot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Fast-Track 'sql' + Alert","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Process 'mql' → HubSpot":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fast-Track 'sql' + Alert":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Merge Routed Work":{"main":[[{"node":"Align Field Names","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Align Field Names":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Processing Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Processing Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Tag Pipeline Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag Pipeline Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (HubSpot)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (HubSpot)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Outlook","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Outlook":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"66f8dc26-cf41-4417-bc7f-52a1f11810f5","id":"FDX04787"}